│ ### Locating the Code                                                                                                                                                                    │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ The issue is in the SLP vectorizer. I need to find the part of the code that decides whether to group instructions for vectorization. A good place to start searching would be files     │
│ related to the SLP vectorizer, likely in `lib/Transforms/Vectorize/`. The file `SLPVectorizer.cpp` is the main file for this pass.                                                       │
